        <abstract>
            <p>Replies to CD’s letter [missing]. He does intend to treat of Pangenesis "as the most remarkable hypothesis yet put forth".</p> 
<p>His articles in <hi rend="italic">Fortnightly Review</hi> have grown in number so that he plans to make a book of them. Asks CD to send him notes of his objections.</p> 
        </abstract>
